sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hku.hk%2Fthink%2Fchi%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=cbd139aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"想真係學邏輯就咪撚用呢個垃圾網啦。果陣hku科non lecture course elementary logic就係用呢個網做course material，個個讀到屌哂鬼。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Patrick J. Hurley本Logic textbook 會比較詳細清晰。但係就冇cover到modal logic，不過新手睇都冇乜問題，同埋有大量exercise。拋下磚，各位連登仔如果有更好選擇不妨share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Concise-Introduction-Logic-Book-Only/dp/0840034164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FConcise-Introduction-Logic-Book-Only%2Fdp%2F0840034164&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=2848ee4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Concise-Introduction-Logic-Book-Only/dp/0840034164</a><br />\n<br />\n申脷: 哲學系grad，就嚟變廢中"},{"pid":"8ca19409c6971a272de29132f0c1b81602bd0afd","tid":2106242,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"讀math<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nreal analysis <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327ed2dd2851f678c0a4c31944e56438f7a72dab","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"740af1a52d92422714bb9dc109d7ce312a07102d","tid":2106242,"uid":105140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5023a6fd2369bace85d5510de36462d9119fab3","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"嗱! 好多人都好廣義地用&quot;邏輯&quot;呢個詞<br />\n如果你係講哲學上的邏輯<br />\n就先由呢度入手啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hku.hk%2Fthink%2Fchi%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=cbd139aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"想真係學邏輯就咪撚用呢個垃圾網啦。果陣hku科non lecture course elementary logic就係用呢個網做course material，個個讀到屌哂鬼。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Patrick J. Hurley本Logic textbook 會比較詳細清晰。但係就冇cover到modal logic，不過新手睇都冇乜問題，同埋有大量exercise。拋下磚，各位連登仔如果有更好選擇不妨share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Concise-Introduction-Logic-Book-Only/dp/0840034164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FConcise-Introduction-Logic-Book-Only%2Fdp%2F0840034164&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=2848ee4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Concise-Introduction-Logic-Book-Only/dp/0840034164</a><br />\n<br />\n申脷: 哲學系grad，就嚟變廢中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"用logic textbook當然係正<br />\n但點樣係冇人教之下 堅持&amp;睇明整本1吋厚的Hurley &amp;做晒D exercise?<br />\n<br />\n我覺得logic係好重要架 尤其現在咁多public speech咁多logical fallacies 更加需要用logic去分辨D說話錯係邊<br />\n自問冇take course 好難跟得好basic logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe5bf4dafb36a0caa479226059bf8232151a8c0","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db07c0724df80950109c947e8412a1db7db33720","tid":2106242,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d5023a6fd2369bace85d5510de36462d9119fab3","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"嗱! 好多人都好廣義地用&quot;邏輯&quot;呢個詞<br />\n如果你係講哲學上的邏輯<br />\n就先由呢度入手啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hku.hk%2Fthink%2Fchi%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=cbd139aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"都差唔多，類似語理分析嗰啲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n數學同邏輯可以點練"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"ching: 唔明呢句 &quot;數學同邏輯可以點練&quot; 你問乜 ？"},{"pid":"400eb58e02d0958fc6692f0556b31c77c2425afb","tid":2106242,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe5bf4dafb36a0caa479226059bf8232151a8c0","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db07c0724df80950109c947e8412a1db7db33720","tid":2106242,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d5023a6fd2369bace85d5510de36462d9119fab3","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"嗱! 好多人都好廣義地用&quot;邏輯&quot;呢個詞<br />\n如果你係講哲學上的邏輯<br />\n就先由呢度入手啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hku.hk%2Fthink%2Fchi%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=cbd139aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"都差唔多，類似語理分析嗰啲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n數學同邏輯可以點練"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"ching: 唔明呢句 &quot;數學同邏輯可以點練&quot; 你問乜 ？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"因為我覺得邏輯好，數學自然好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望train好啲邏輯，遲下再讀返書如果要用到數學，姐係微積分嗰啲會用得著<br />\n<br />\n而呢家想練好啲邏輯純粹係平時返工被人話做嘢唔make sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />姐係好似唔夠醒目咁"},{"pid":"7fcc6902b451d5d1bdd65f9159e6a0d0334a7615","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"400eb58e02d0958fc6692f0556b31c77c2425afb","tid":2106242,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe5bf4dafb36a0caa479226059bf8232151a8c0","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db07c0724df80950109c947e8412a1db7db33720","tid":2106242,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"都差唔多，類似語理分析嗰啲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n數學同邏輯可以點練"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"ching: 唔明呢句 &quot;數學同邏輯可以點練&quot; 你問乜 ？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"因為我覺得邏輯好，數學自然好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望train好啲邏輯，遲下再讀返書如果要用到數學，姐係微積分嗰啲會用得著<br />\n<br />\n而呢家想練好啲邏輯純粹係平時返工被人話做嘢唔make sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />姐係好似唔夠醒目咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"ching: <br />\n邏輯&amp;maths係兩樣野<br />\nLogic is a basic knowledge (a basic subject) in philosophy. <br />\nYou don't need maths to study philosophy except you study philosophy of maths (數學的哲學).<br />\n<br />\n你講緊既: 講野冇common sense係語意邏輯 &mdash; 即係一段說話中, 有冇前後矛盾/前文不能推出結論/文章內容不合乎常理/將冇關連的事放在一起然後推論等等<br />\n<br />\n先舉D例︰<br />\n1. 出面落緊雨, 但個地冇濕。=&gt;不合乎常理<br />\n2. 我冇女朋友，所以呀媽煮飯。=&gt;兩者並無關/前者不能推出結論<br />\n3. 呀X係2010年1月1 日5pm又出現在尖咀又出現係上水。=&gt; 犯了principle of non-contradiction<br />\n<br />\n以上冇一句與數學有關的<br />\n要訓練語意邏輯/發現日常有乜野有邏輯問題 可以睇書 但 我唔識呢類書 或請其他ching推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7898cb97eefbdf9dc194038058352541a5c5900","tid":2106242,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"400eb58e02d0958fc6692f0556b31c77c2425afb","tid":2106242,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe5bf4dafb36a0caa479226059bf8232151a8c0","tid":2106242,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db07c0724df80950109c947e8412a1db7db33720","tid":2106242,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:39:22.0